title: On Vladimir Nabokov
description:
The torrent contains the following book; all books are in Pdf format:


Chasing Lolita- Graham Vickers
Discourse and Ideology in Nabokov's Prose- David Larmour
Figurations of Exile- Professor Barbara Straumann
Imagining Nabokov- Nina L. Khrushcheva
Marvell, Nabokov- Childhood and Arcadia- Michael Long
Nabokov and his Fiction, New Perspectives- Julian W. Connolly
Nabokov's Permanent Mystery- David S. Rutledge
Stalking Nabokov- Selected Essays- Brian Boyd (epub+ PDF)
The American Years- Brian Boyd
The Cambridge Companion to Nabokov- Julian W. Connolly
The Russian Years- Brian Boyd
The Secret History of Vladimir Nabokov- Andrea Pitzer
The World of Nabokov's Stories- Maxim D. Shrayer
Vladimir Nabokov and the Art of Painting- Gerard de Vries and D. Barton Johnson
Vladimir Nabokov- Barbara Wyllie
